Package onbon.y2.http Description

The HTTP interface defines the ways to communicate to the Y2.
There are 2 implementations, one is y2-http-hc, the other is y2-http-ok.
y2-http-hc uses Apache HttpComponents. This driver works on JDK 6+, but does not work on the Android.
y2-http-ok uses OkHttp. This driver works on JDK8 and the Android.
